---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Cookie Policy">
  <main class="policy-container">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="policy-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <h1>Cookie Policy</h1>
        <p class="last-updated">Last Updated: May 22, 2026</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Content -->
    <section class="policy-content">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="policy-text">
          <h2>1. What Are Cookies?</h2>
          <p>
            Cookies are small data files that are placed on your device (computer, tablet, or mobile phone) when you visit a website or use an app. They help websites and apps remember information about your visit, such as your preferences and login details.
          </p>

          <h2>2. Cookies We Use</h2>
          <p>
            Fluly uses cookies and similar tracking technologies to enhance your experience, analyze how you use the Service, and provide personalized content. We use the following types of cookies:
          </p>

          <h3>Essential Cookies</h3>
          <p>
            These cookies are necessary for the Service to function properly. They enable you to navigate the website and use essential features like account login and content management. Without these cookies, the Service may not work as expected.
          </p>

          <h3>Analytics Cookies</h3>
          <p>
            We use Google Analytics for Firebase to collect information about how you use the Service. This helps us understand user behavior, improve our features, and enhance your experience. These cookies collect anonymous data such as page visits and user interactions.
          </p>

          <h3>Preference Cookies</h3>
          <p>
            These cookies remember your preferences and settings, such as language choice, theme preferences, and other customizations you've made while using the Service.
          </p>

          <h3>Marketing Cookies</h3>
          <p>
            We may use cookies to track the effectiveness of our marketing campaigns and to deliver targeted advertisements that are relevant to your interests.
          </p>

          <h2>3. Third-Party Cookies</h2>
          <p>
            Some cookies are placed by third-party services that we use, including:
          </p>
          <ul class="policy-list">
            <li><strong>Firebase (Google):</strong> For analytics, authentication, and performance monitoring</li>
            <li><strong>YouTube:</strong> For embedding video content</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>4. How We Use Cookie Data</h2>
          <p>
            The information collected through cookies is used to:
          </p>
          <ul class="policy-list">
            <li>Keep you logged in and maintain your session</li>
            <li>Remember your preferences and settings</li>
            <li>Analyze usage patterns and improve the Service</li>
            <li>Detect and prevent fraud or security issues</li>
            <li>Deliver personalized content and recommendations</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>5. Your Cookie Choices</h2>
          <p>
            Most browsers allow you to control cookies through settings. You can set your browser to refuse all cookies or to alert you when cookies are being sent. However, disabling cookies may affect the functionality of the Service.
          </p>

          <h3>Opt-Out Options</h3>
          <p>
            You can opt out of Google Analytics tracking by visiting <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google's Analytics Opt-out Browser Add-on</a>.
          </p>

          <h2>6. Data Retention</h2>
          <p>
            Cookies are typically retained for varying periods depending on their purpose. Essential cookies may persist as long as you use the Service, while analytics cookies are typically retained for analysis periods and then deleted.
          </p>

          <h2>7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p>
            Fluly may update this Cookie Policy from time to time. We recommend reviewing this policy periodically to stay informed about how we use cookies.
          </p>

          <h2>8. Contact Us</h2>
          <p>
            If you have questions about our use of cookies or this Cookie Policy, please contact us at: <a href="mailto:reikomlive@gmail.com">reikomlive@gmail.com</a>
          </p>

          <h2>9. Legal Basis</h2>
          <p>
            We use cookies based on our legitimate interests in improving the Service and providing a better user experience. For non-essential cookies, we rely on your consent, which you can withdraw at any time through your browser settings or our opt-out mechanisms.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .policy-container {
    background-color: #0a0520;
    color: #e5e7eb;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
  }

  /* Hero Section */
  .policy-hero {
    padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2d2a5f 0%, #1a0f3d 100%);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(168, 157, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .policy-hero h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #a78bfa, #7c3aed);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .last-updated {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #9ca3af;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Content Section */
  .policy-content {
    padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
  }

  .policy-text {
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .policy-text h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: #a78bfa;
    margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .policy-text h2:first-child {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .policy-text h3 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #c4b5fd;
    margin: 1.5rem 0 0.75rem;
  }

  .policy-text p {
    color: #d1d5db;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .policy-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 1rem 0;
  }

  .policy-list li {
    color: #d1d5db;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .policy-list li::before {
    content: '•';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #a78bfa;
  }

  .policy-text a {
    color: #a78bfa;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .policy-text a:hover {
    color: #c4b5fd;
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .policy-hero h1 {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
    }

    .policy-text h2 {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }
  }
</style>
